OL,3,CHow UV rays cause sunburn - and why
OL,4,Csun cream still matters in spring
OL,6,FThe sun in spring has the same
OL,7,Fstrength as it does in late summer, so
OL,8,Fif you're waiting to feel hot before
OL,9,Fyou reach for the SPF, you're sure to
OL,10,Fend up red-faced.
OL,12,FHere's everything you need to know to
OL,13,Fkeep yourselves and your loved ones
OL,14,Fsafe.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,21,FWhat actually is UV?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
