OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776942175
OL,3,CHow UV rays cause sunburn - and why
OL,4,Csun cream still matters in spring
OL,6,F"UV" refers to ultraviolet radiation -
OL,7,Fa form of electromagnetic energy
OL,8,Fnaturally emitted by the sun that can
OL,9,Fpenetrate the skin and cause effects
OL,10,Flike burning and long-term skin damage.
OL,12,FUV radiation is also produced by
OL,13,Fartificial sources like tanning beds
OL,14,Fand certain lamps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776942175
OL,3,CHow UV rays cause sunburn - and why
OL,4,Csun cream still matters in spring
OL,6,FThere are several types of UV, but
OL,7,Fthose most linked to skin cancer are
OL,8,FUVA, which penetrates deep into the
OL,9,Fskin - linked to wrinkles and ageing
OL,10,Fand long-term damage - and UVB which
OL,11,Faffects the surface of the skin
OL,12,Fcausing sunburn and plays a key role
OL,13,Fin skin cancer.
OL,15,FWhy is it dangerous to get sunburnt?
OL,17,FIn the short term, sunburn is an
OL,18,Finflammatory injury.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
