OL,3,CHow UV rays cause sunburn - and why
OL,4,Csun cream still matters in spring
OL,6,FThis is where a lot of people get
OL,7,Fcaught out.
OL,9,FThe risk of sunburn has nothing to do
OL,10,Fwith temperature and everything to do
OL,11,Fwith the strength of the sun.
OL,13,FSkiers wear sunblock on the slopes
OL,14,Fwhen temperatures are well below
OL,15,Ffreezing - and many of us have been
OL,16,Fcaught out on a bright day with a cold
OL,17,Fwind that made it feel quite chilly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
